title: Bonus: Live from the White House Correspondents’ Dinner
description: Mark Warner, Asa Hutchinson, Roy Wood Jr. and more join Playbook co-author Ryan Lizza and CBS News’ Major Garrett for a live broadcast from the White House Correspondents’ Dinner.

title: Leonard Leo used Federalist Society contact to obtain $1.6B donation
description: The society’s close ties to Leo’s network raise questions about its nonpartisan, non-political status.
